{"word":"G588 - ἀποδέχομαι - apodéchomai - ap-od-ekh'-om-ahee - Accept","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποδέχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apodéchomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-od-ekh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Accept</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பெற்றுக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"receive"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G1209 - δέχομαι - déchomai - dekh'-om-ahee/1209\">G1209</a>; to <i>take fully</i>, that is, <i>welcome</i> (persons), <i>approve</i> (things): - accept, receive (gladly).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1184/1184\">G1184</a>, <a href=\"#/G1209/1209\">G1209</a>, <a href=\"#/G1403/1403\">G1403</a>, <a href=\"#/G1523/1523\">G1523</a>, <a href=\"#/G1561/1561\">G1561</a>, <a href=\"#/G2144/2144\">G2144</a>, <a href=\"#/G4327/4327\">G4327</a>, <a href=\"#/G553/553\">G553</a>, <a href=\"#/G587/587\">G587</a>, <a href=\"#/G588/588\">G588</a>, <a href=\"#/G594/594\">G594</a>"}]}